            <title>1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 10:07:44 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## New

- **Automatic updates.** Setcraft now checks for new versions on its own and can
  install them for you, so you stay current without downloading and dragging a
  new copy by hand. Check anytime from Help, Check for Updates.

Includes everything from 1.1.0 (Local Backup, the Backstage reorganization, and
the accessibility and copy pass) for anyone coming from an earlier build.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
